---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-invert">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">How to Speed Up a Slow Computer in 2026</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">July 2026 • RigRescue Helpful Tips</p>

            <p>Is your computer feeling sluggish? Before buying new hardware, try these common fixes that often make a dramatic difference.</p>

            <h2>Quick & Effective Fixes</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Clean up temporary files, cache, and bloatware</li>
                <li>Run a full malware scan</li>
                <li>Upgrade to an SSD if you're still using a traditional hard drive (this is usually the biggest performance boost you can get)</li>
                <li>Update your drivers and Windows</li>
                <li>Reduce startup programs (you can still launch them manually when needed)</li>
                <li>Install any pending Windows updates</li>
                <li>Simple restart — this fixes more issues than you'd think!</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>When It's Time for Professional Help</h2>
            <p>If the above steps don’t bring satisfying results, a full diagnostic and optimization from RigRescue can make a big difference — often done remotely.</p>

            <div class="text-center mt-12">
                <a href="/contact"
                   class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-medium">
                    Book a Performance Tune-Up
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
